EXTENDED PREAMBLE

The Royal bot is more than just software—it is a philosophy of freedom,
collaboration, and empowerment in the digital community. By using,
sharing, or modifying Royal, you agree to uphold the principles of open
access, transparency, and ethical conduct. This license is designed to
ensure that Royal, and any derivative works, remain free and open,
allowing every user to benefit from its features while respecting the
rights of the original creator, Mudau Thendo.

Royal is intended to be used responsibly. Misuse, misrepresentation, or
any action that harms the community or other users is strictly
discouraged. This extended license explains in detail your rights,
responsibilities, and limitations when interacting with the Royal bot.

By reading this license, you acknowledge the following principles:

1. Freedom to Use: You may run Royal for any purpose, personal or
   commercial, without restriction.

2. Freedom to Study: You may study how Royal works and make modifications
   to fit your own needs, while crediting the original creators.

3. Freedom to Share: You may distribute copies of Royal in unmodified
   or modified form to others, ensuring that it remains free and open.

4. Freedom to Collaborate: Contributions to Royal are encouraged, provided
   that the license terms are followed.

