2. "You" or "Licensee" refers to any individual or organization that
   receives, uses, modifies, or redistributes Royal.

3. "Modification" refers to any changes made to Royal's source code,
   configuration, media, or documentation.

4. "Distribution" refers to sharing Royal, in source or compiled form,
   with any third party.

5. "Community" refers to all users, contributors, and maintainers
   involved with Royal.

6. "Derivative Work" refers to any work based upon Royal that is modified,
   enhanced, or extended in any way.

