RESPONSIBILITIES AND ETHICS

1. You must include this LICENSE in all copies or derivative works
   you distribute.

2. You must clearly indicate any changes or modifications made to Royal.

3. You must not remove or alter copyright notices or licensing information.

4. You must respect the Royal community and avoid harmful conduct,
   including but not limited to:
   a. Deleting critical features without disclosure.
   b. Using Royal for harassment, phishing, or malware distribution.
   c. Claiming Royal as your original work without proper attribution.

5. You must notify the community or original author of critical
   vulnerabilities or bugs, especially if you distribute modified versions.

6. You must avoid tagging mods, guards, or other community members
   unnecessarily or maliciously within Royal bot commands.

